OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598699
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,FWhich? found several products that
OL,8,Fwere cheaper at Waitrose, including
OL,9,FAmoy Straight To Wok Noodles, which
OL,10,Fwere on average #1.25 at both Waitrose
OL,11,Fand Morrisons but most expensive at
OL,12,FSainsbury's and Tesco without a
OL,13,Floyalty card at an average of #2.15 `
OL,14,Fa 72% difference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598699
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,FSea salt and vinegar Ryvita Thins were
OL,8,Falso cheapest on average at Waitrose
OL,9,Fat #1.25, but shoppers buying this
OL,10,Fproduct at Morrisons, Tesco, and
OL,11,FSainsbury's without a loyalty card
OL,12,Fwould all have paid an average of
OL,13,F#2.30, making them 84% more expensive.
OL,15,FFor customers with a Clubcard, Which?
OL,16,Ffound that the same list of groceries
OL,17,Fat Tesco fell to #837.43 on average `
OL,18,Fjust 2% more expensive than Asda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598699
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,FWhich? found various instances of
OL,8,Fbranded products where the Tesco
OL,9,FClubcard price was the cheapest on
OL,10,Faverage.
OL,12,FCarex Hand Wash was 95p at Tesco with
OL,13,Fa Clubcard but #1.70 at Waitrose where
OL,14,Fit was the most expensive.
OL,16,FAnother example showed Kellogg's
OL,17,FCrunchy Nut cornflakes was #1.55 on
OL,18,Faverage in February, while the highest
OL,19,Faverage price among the supermarkets
OL,20,Fwas at Waitrose where it cost #2.50.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
