OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598699
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,F"If you've got your heart set on
OL,8,Fspecific brands, your best bet is to
OL,9,Fshop around, keep a close eye on the
OL,10,Funit price, and stock up whenever you
OL,11,Fsee a good deal ` otherwise, you're
OL,12,Flikely to end up paying way over the
OL,13,Fodds.
OL,15,F"While loyalty cards definitely offer
OL,16,Fsome savings, if you don't use one
OL,17,Fyou're better off heading to Asda,
OL,18,Fwhere the pricing is usually cheaper
OL,19,Fon a range of branded goods."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
