PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598700
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,FA Sainsbury's spokesman said: "We have
OL,8,Finvested over #1 billion in recent
OL,9,Fyears to help keep prices low and we
OL,10,Fknow more customers are choosing to do
OL,11,Ftheir shop at Sainsbury's.
OL,13,F"We are committed to helping customers
OL,14,Faccess great quality at lower prices
OL,15,Fand remain focused on offering
OL,16,Foutstanding value across thousands of
OL,17,Fproducts through our Aldi price match
OL,18,Fscheme, Nectar prices, Your Nectar
OL,19,FPrices and our own-brand value lines."
OL,26,@oD@_OUuD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
