CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774598700
OL,3,CTesco and Sainsbury's non-loyalty
OL,4,Cbrand prices more expensive than
OL,5,CWaitrose
OL,7,FA spokesman for Tesco said: "It's no
OL,8,Fsecret that Tesco Clubcard unlocks
OL,9,Fexceptional savings for the 24 million
OL,10,FUK households who have one.
OL,12,F"More than 80% of our sales are made
OL,13,Fwith a Clubcard ` but it's just one of
OL,14,Fthe ways our customers get great value.
OL,16,F"Though everyday low prices we keep
OL,17,Fprices consistently low on thousands
OL,18,Fof branded products, and our Aldi
OL,19,Fprice match ensures shoppers can be
OL,20,Fconfident they're getting competitive
OL,21,Fprices."
